 Product Development Jobs in Akron  At FirstEnergy we offer our 15,500 employees significant opportunities to build challenging and rewarding careers. Why apply for Product Development jobs in Akron at FirstEnergy? FirstEnergy is a forward-thinking electric utility powered by a diverse team of employees committed to making customers’ lives brighter, the environment better and our communities stronger. The leadership, skills, diversity and character of our employees have helped FirstEnergy become a successful Fortune 200 company. And we’re looking for more talented people who will contribute to our future success. Our goal is to provide a work environment where you can expect innovation, strong leadership, accountability, and integrity – and where your efforts will be rewarded. Explore Product Development jobs in Akron at FirstEnergy. Join our Talent Network to receive updates about jobs that match your interests.











